OL,6,FAs more and more money pours into the
OL,7,Ffight against climate change and
OL,8,Fbiodiversity loss, tree planting in
OL,9,FBritain is booming.
OL,11,FBusinesses see it as a way to do good
OL,12,Fand burnish their image or simply to
OL,13,Fprofit from subsidies, while
OL,14,Fministers see it as a relatively
OL,15,Fcheap and quick way to store carbon
OL,16,Fand create habitat.
OL,18,FMinisters have promised that Britain
OL,19,Fwill be planting 30 million trees a
OL,20,Fyear by 2024, with much of that
OL,21,Ffigure coming from private companies.
OL,3,CWhy planting trees can sometimes be
OL,4,Cthe wrong answer to climate change
